name: Dimples- The Last Laugh 3
description:
Physical copies of GFam member Dimples huge mixtape The Last Laugh 3 are finally available and Dimples has dropped us some copies to post on our bigcartel today.

Featuring 20 massive tracks including This and That, Peak Freestyle and the huge anthem Groundwork the mixtape also has features from his fellow GFam buddies as well as Neeko, Big Narstie, Nico Lindsay, Black The Ripper and more plus productions ranging from Flava D to Dexplicit, order your copy today!!

Tracks:

1.Intro

2.Policeman ft Nico Lindsay, Marger & Fumin 

3.This And That

4.KissFm Freestyle [Radio Rip]

5.Bloodclart

6.Peak [Freestyle]

7.Music Star

8.Blaze Em ft Rival

9.No Doubt

10.Groundwork ft Big Narstie, Neeko, Calibar, Black The Ripper, J Money, Random Impulse & Rival

11.Groundwork [Rude Kid Remix, Radio 1 Rip]

12.100 Raindrops

13.New Flava

14.Seagulls ft Sicx, Random Impulse & Styler

15.Ghost Train

16.Bad Attitude

17.1xtra Freestyle [Tim Westwood]

18.96 Bars Of Remembrance

19.Shakedown ft Joe Black & Sups

20.Outro

name: MOG & GFam Records Present Styler - Perfect Timing EP
description:
Having linked up with GFams Styler were now pleased to be able to bring you physical copies of the Perfect Timing EP.

The Perfect Timing EP is 5 tracks deep including 'Bye' 'In The City' 'Home Alone' and the massive 'Styles' as well as features from the likes of fellow GFam buddes Dimples and Sicx, Rival, Nico Lindsay and Kwam and productions from HK, Skillioso, Chillz and Spooky.

Tracklist:

1.Styles (prod by Dj Spooky)

2.Home Alone ft Nico Lindsay (prod by HK)

3.Bye (prod by Skillioso)

4.In The City ft Dimples and Rival (prod by Chillz)

5.Cant Tell Me Nothing ft Sicx and Kwam (prod by Krimson)

First 10 people to order Perfect Timing EP receive a free tee so get ordering!!!
